features: NATURAL CAT FLEA AND TICK SUPPORT: Our cat flea and tick chews are made with natural ingredients and offer a pet-friendly, gentle addition to support comfort from common seasonal factors, helping keep your cat at ease. This expert-formulated formula provides gentle daily chewable supplements for cats and kittens. Each can contains 200 chews, offering over 3 months of use

DAILY CARE, ONGOING SUPPORT: Woyamay cat flea chews provide daily care and offer gentle support for comfort during seasonal changes and outdoor exposure. These chews are designed as part of a regular routine for cats of all sizes. A pet-friendly, easy-to-use option compared to drops, sprays, or shampoos

DAILY SUPPORT WITH NATURAL INGREDIENTS: Our daily chewable cat treats are made with naturally derived ingredients and are suitable for cats of all breeds and ages. Each soft chew contains coconut oil, flaxseed, and brewer's yeast, and includes no harsh chemicals or artificial additives. Gentle for both kittens and senior cats, these chews offer a mild, routine-friendly option for everyday care

SKIN & COAT CARE: Our flea and tick support chews for cats are formulated with skin-nourishing ingredients, including fish oil and B vitamins. These chews help hydrate your cat's skin while supporting a smooth, glossy coat. With consistent use, they support coat appearance and offer gentle daily support during seasonal changes

DELICIOUS & EASY TO USE: Our Woyamay cat and kitten flea support chews feature a delicious chicken flavor that even picky eaters will love. They are easy to administer—simply offer them as a snack or crush and mix them into a meal for effortless serving. Our tasty chicken-flavored chewables make daily flea support for kittens and cats a treat, not a chore
